# Enforce LF line endings on Markdown so the workflow-gate + build-evidence
# hooks (which anchor on `^## Workflow$`, `### Checklist`, etc.) match on
# downstream Windows checkouts. A CRLF state.md would otherwise fail the
# `^## Workflow$` anchor and silently bypass every gate. The hooks also strip
# \r defensively, but normalizing at checkout is the first line of defense.
*.md text eol=lf
state.md text eol=lf
